2025-07-07 15:21:46.343 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (123ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT m."Id", m."Email", m."IsDeleted", m."Name", p."Id", p."CreatedByEmail", p."Description", p."EndDate", p."IsDeleted", p."PoleFileId", p."StartDate", p."Title"
FROM "Moderators" AS m
